'''Miyazaki Shrine''' (宮崎神社, pronounced *Miyazaki Jinja*) refers to various Shinto shrines across Japan.
* {{ill|Miyazaki Jingū|ja|宮崎神宮|12=draft|12=draft}} - Formerly known as Miyazaki Jingu. * {{ill|Miyazaki Shrine (Rikuzentakata)|ja|宮崎神社 (陸前高田市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Rikuzentakata|ja|陸前高田市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Iwate Prefecture|ja|岩手県|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Miyazaki Shrine (Okazaki)|ja|宮崎神社 (岡崎市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Okazaki|ja|岡崎市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Aichi Prefecture|ja|愛知県|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Miyazaki Shrine (Akitakata)|ja|宮崎神社 (安芸高田市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Akitakata|ja|安芸高田市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Hiroshima Prefecture|ja|広島県|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Miyazaki Shrine (Akune)|ja|宮崎神社 (阿久根市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Akune|ja|阿久根市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Kagoshima Prefecture|ja|鹿児島県|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Miyazaki Shrine (Kagoshima)|ja|宮崎神社 (鹿児島市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Kagoshima|ja|鹿児島市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Kagoshima Prefecture. * {{ill|Miyazaki Shrine (Higashihiroshima)|ja|宮崎神社 (東広島市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Higashihiroshima|ja|東広島市|12=draft|12=draft}}, Hiroshima Prefecture. * {{ill|Miyazaki Shrine (Daisen)|ja|宮崎神社 (大栄町)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Daisen|ja|大栄町|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Tottori Prefecture|ja|鳥取県|12=draft|12=draft}}.
